Har har Poison gjort en coverplatta dar de tolkar sina favoriter. Vi hittar bl a Little Willy (Sweet), Suffragette City (Bowie) Rock And Roll All Nite (Kiss), Squeeze Box (Who), I Never Cry (Alice Cooper), I Need To Know (Tom Petty), We&#039;re An American Band (Grand Funk) och Dead Flowers (Rolling Stones).
